vulnerability.name: USN-6139-1
vulnerability.description: Yebo Cao discovered that Python incorrectly handled certain URLs. An attacker could use this issue to bypass blockinglisting methods. This issue was first addressed in USN-5960-1, but was incomplete. Here we address an additional fix to that issue. (CVE-2023-24329)

statements.status_notes: Python could be made to bypass blocklisting methods if a specially crafted URL was provided
